VPNId.name: VPNId
VPNId.description: The purpose of a VPN-ID is to identify a VPN. The global VPN Identifier format is: 3 octet VPN Authority, Organizationally Unique Identifier followed by 4 octet VPN index identifying VPN according to OUI
VPNId.reference: RFC 2685, Fox & Gleeson, 'Virtual Private Networks Identifier', September 1999.
